headline: Atmos: Fiscal Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: DALLAS (AP) — Atmos Energy Corp. ATO) on Wednesday reported fiscal fourth-quarter earnings of $134 million. The Dallas-based company said it had net income of 86 cents per share.
